图/法新文 | 徐进是的！好转迹象就藏在数据更新中。
Photo / AFP / AT & # 45; # 124; & # 45; & # 45; Yes! Signs of improvement are hidden in the update.
据国家和湖北省卫健委公布的数据，截止到2月5日24时，有关数据分析如下：1、新增确诊病例数由陡增转为下降其中湖北新增确诊病例数结束连续一周的“步步高”由升转降尤为可贵。
As of 2400 hours Feb. 5, the data analysed were as follows: 1. The number of newly confirmed cases has changed from sharp increase to decrease.
难免有反复，但确是标志性的，表明近几日湖北、武汉全力提升检测能力、收治能力初见成效，“堰塞湖”正在化解。
Inevitably there are repeated, but it is a landmark, showing that in recent days Hubei, Wuhan to improve the capacity of detection, treatment capacity is beginning to show results, "Yan Sehu" is being resolved.
图（1）2、确诊病例增长率继续下降说到拐点，必须关注增长率的变化。
Chart (1) The Growth Rate of Confirmed Cases Continues to Decline When it comes to the inflection point, we must pay attention to the change of growth rate.
增长率降为零才是决定性的。
A zero growth rate is decisive.
我们看到全国确诊病例增长率从最初的50%以上一路下行。
We have seen a downward trend in the national rate of confirmed cases from over 50 per cent.
非湖北地区的增长率第一次降到10%以下；湖北的增长率第一次降到20%以下。
For the first time, the growth rate in non-Hubei region fell below 10%, and that of Hubei dropped below 20% for the first time.
10%、20%仍然很高，但毕竟趋势已显。
Ten per cent and 20 per cent are still high, but the trend is clear.
图（2）3、待排查疑似病例数趋稳图（3）4、治愈人数远超病死人数累计治愈出院人数与病死人数继续拉大差距图（4）。
Fig. (2) Diagram 3: Number of Suspected Cases to be Settled Down Diagram 4. The number of people cured far exceeds the number of people who died of diseases.
湖北也在近日实现了治愈人数反超病死人数图（5）。
Hubei also recently achieved the number of cured number of anti-superdisease death figure (5).
病死率趋降。
The fatality rate is declining.
非湖北地区的病死率低于流感图（6）。
The mortality rate of non-Hubei area was lower than that of influenza map (6).
图（4）图（5）图（6）初步结论：拐点正在到来，我们仍需努力。
Figure (4) Figure (5) Figure (6) Preliminary conclusion: The inflection point is coming and we still need to make efforts.
